## 1. Agreement to Terms

Welcome to Akrondis! These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the Akrondis countdown converter service operated by Akrondis Company, a Philippines-based company. By accessing or using our service, you agree to be bound by these Terms.

## 2. Description of Service

Akrondis is a web-based tool that:
- Converts UTC timestamps to Discord-formatted countdown timers
- Helps accountability Discord groups track goal deadlines
- Provides user account management through Google authentication
- Stores user goals and Discord nicknames for personalized service

## 3. User Accounts and Registration

### 3.1 Account Creation
